1971;;Freelance;;British;;Francis Megahy;;Ian McShane, Gayle Hunnicutt;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freelance_(1971_film);;Mitch (McShane) is a London con-artist. When he witnesses a gangland hit, he is forced to lie low whilst trying to carry out his own various schemes. The film offers a portrayal of early 1970s west London.